<HL>
   U.S. Justice Department Seeks to Block
   Sale of Semiconductor Firm to Japanese
   ----
   By Paul M. Barrett
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
12/31/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE 10
</SO>
